OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FSix of the Lionesses, rugby league
OL,7,Fgreat Kevin Sinfield and actress Dame
OL,8,FHelen Mirren have all featured in the
OL,9,FKing's Birthday Honours list.
OL,11,FChloe Kelly, who scored the winning
OL,12,Fpenalty in last summer's nail-biting
OL,13,FEuros final, was made an MBE alongside
OL,14,Fgoalkeeper Hannah Hampton, defender
OL,15,FJess Carter and forwards Alessia
OL,16,FRusso, Lauren James and Michelle
OL,17,FAgyemang.
OL,19,FAt 20, Agyemang is the youngest
OL,20,Frecipient on the list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
