OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FFormer England captain Sinfield was
OL,7,Fknighted after completing six running
OL,8,Fchallenges to raise more than #10
OL,9,Fmillion for motor neurone disease
OL,10,F(MND) charities following the death of
OL,11,Fhis former Leeds Rhinos team-mate Rob
OL,12,FBurrow.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FBurrow died in 2024 after living with
OL,20,FMND for more than four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
