OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781359876
OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,F"I am deeply honoured and grateful to
OL,7,Freceive this award on behalf of the
OL,8,Frugby and MND communities," Sinfield
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Since I first played rugby when I was
OL,12,Fseven, rugby league has given me so
OL,13,Fmuch. I am particularly proud to
OL,14,Ffollow in the footsteps of the great
OL,15,FSir Billy Boston with rugby league's
OL,16,Fsecond-ever knighthood in over 130
OL,17,Fyears of the sport.
OL,19,F"Sir Billy overcame so much in his
OL,20,Flife and is still loved by the game."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]sD@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
