OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FSinfield is taking on his seventh and
OL,7,Ffinal endurance challenge ` all of
OL,8,Fwhich have been based around the
OL,9,Fnumber seven as it was the number
OL,10,FBurrow wore in his playing days ` in
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FLindsey Burrow, widow of Rob Burrow,
OL,14,Fsaid: "On behalf of the whole Burrow
OL,15,Ffamily, I would like to congratulate
OL,16,FKevin on his knighthood. We are all
OL,17,Fdelighted for him and I cannot think
OL,18,Fof a more deserving recipient.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
