OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781359876
OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,F"Kevin did so much for Rob but also
OL,7,Fthe whole MND community with raising
OL,8,Fawareness and funds to support
OL,9,Ffamilies and aid research.
OL,11,FI know he has said he is dedicated to
OL,12,Fsupporting the MND community for
OL,13,Fhowever long it takes to find a cure,
OL,14,Fand that means so much to so many
OL,15,Fpeople to have a champion like Kevin
OL,16,Fin their corner.
OL,18,F"As Rob used to say, everyone should
OL,19,Fhave a friend like Kevin and so many
OL,20,Fpeople will be pleased to see him get
OL,21,Fthis recognition."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU}D@RO]
