OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FActor Dame Helen Mirren, who won an
OL,7,FOscar for her portrayal of the Queen
OL,8,Fin 2006, was also made a Companion of
OL,9,FHonour for services to drama.
OL,11,FThere are only 65 Companions of Honour
OL,12,Fat any one time.
OL,14,FNearly 1,200 people from across the UK
OL,15,Freceived honours in the latest list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
