OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FBlack Sabbath guitarist Tony Iommi
OL,7,Fbecame an MBE for his services to
OL,8,Fmusic and charity, and Emmerdale
OL,9,Factress Lisa Riley received the same
OL,10,Fhonour for her services to drama and
OL,11,Fher charity work.
OL,13,F"What an unbelievable honour to
OL,14,Freceive an MBE. It's been a privilege
OL,15,Fdoing something I love and then to see
OL,16,Fthat music connects with so many over
OL,17,Fthe years," said Iommi.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
