OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FRiley, who turns 50 in July, said:
OL,7,F"Wow, if this is not my best 50th
OL,8,Fbirthday present, being awarded an MBE
OL,9,Fin the King's Birthday Honours list, I
OL,10,Fdon't know what is. To say I am
OL,11,Fhumbled is an absolute understatement.
OL,13,F"Thank you so much, my heart is the
OL,14,Fwarmest it could ever be."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUvD@ZO]
