OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FDavid Sproxton and Peter Lord, the co-
OL,7,Ffounders of the Academy Award-winning
OL,8,Fanimation studio behind beloved
OL,9,Fcharacters such as Wallace and Gromit
OL,10,Fand Shaun the Sheep, were both
OL,11,Fknighted for their services to the
OL,12,Fcreative industries and to charity.
OL,14,F"We both feel it is an extraordinary
OL,15,Fprivilege and an honour ` as well as a
OL,16,Fcomplete and utter surprise ` to be
OL,17,Frecognised in this way," the duo said
OL,18,Fin a statement.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
