OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781359876
OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,F"As we accept these awards, we humbly
OL,7,Fbow and salute all of those who have
OL,8,Fjoined us on this extraordinary
OL,9,Fjourney."
OL,11,FThe Gruffalo writer Julia Donaldson
OL,12,Fand Noughts and Crosses author Malorie
OL,13,FBlackman both received damehoods for
OL,14,Ftheir services to literature.
OL,16,FDame Julia was the UK's best-selling
OL,17,Fauthor last year, overtaking Harry
OL,18,FPotter creator JK Rowling amid the
OL,19,FGruffalo's continued popularity and
OL,20,Fthe success of more recent characters
OL,21,Flike Zog the dragon.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]
