OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FShe said: "Receiving this honour has
OL,7,Fbeen a very happy surprise. It's
OL,8,Freally gratifying to have children's
OL,9,Fbooks recognised in this way."
OL,11,FBeauty entrepreneur and make-up artist
OL,12,Fto the stars, Charlotte Tilbury, was
OL,13,Falso made a Commander of the Order of
OL,14,Fthe British Empire (CBE).
OL,16,FThe oldest recipient was 101-year-old
OL,17,FPauline Hough, who received a British
OL,18,FEmpire Medal (BEM) for services to
OL,19,Ftheatre and to the community in
OL,20,FNantwich, Cheshire.
