OL,3,CRugby star Kevin Sinfield and six
OL,4,Clionesses lead King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,7,F"Across the UK, people are quietly
OL,8,Fchanging lives and strengthening their
OL,9,Fcommunities. This Honours List is a
OL,10,Fchance to recognise them.
OL,12,FTheir dedication shows how lasting
OL,13,Fchange is built ` through compassion,
OL,14,Fresilience and a commitment to others.
OL,16,F"It speaks to the decent, hopeful
OL,17,Fcountry we are proud to be, and on
OL,18,Fbehalf of the whole nation, I want to
OL,19,Fsay thank you."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU{D@OO]
